      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically still has that new-car smell! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been pampered and is ready to hit the road without a single worry, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
