    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a comprehensive mechanical pedigree, including a documented VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory helical limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, bolstered by refreshed bushings and high-fidelity dampers for optimal turn-in response. Meticulously maintained with an immaculate undercarriage and flawless exterior finish, this is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
