    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish with zero imperfections, swirls, or rock chips, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, fading, or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive, documented maintenance history included in the sale. Garage-kept since day one and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as though it just rolled off the assembly line. Every electronic feature, sensor, and accessory functions exactly as intended.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
